# Spotter — Environment Variables
#
# These are NOT required for basic usage. Spotter stores all credentials
# in its local SQLite database via the Profile screen.
#
# Set XDG_DATA_HOME to override the default data directory:
# XDG_DATA_HOME=/path/to/custom/dir
#
# ── Platform API keys (configured in Spotter's Profile UI) ──
#
# Steam: Get an API key at https://steamcommunity.com/dev/apikey
# STEAM_API_KEY=
#
# Xbox: Get a free API key at https://xbl.io
# XBOX_API_KEY=
#
# PlayStation: Get NPSSO token from https://ca.account.sony.com/api/v1/ssocookie
# PSN_NPSSO=
#
# GOG: Uses OAuth login flow — no manual API key needed
